WEBVTT

00:03:29.207 --> 00:03:36.167
I take this capillary and stick it
on to the Paperfuge with some tape.

00:03:38.967 --> 00:03:45.967
Now with my hands when I rotate
this centrifuge for just 90 seconds,

00:03:46.607 --> 00:03:53.607
it can separate the blood in the plasma,
the red blood cells and its components.

00:03:59.527 --> 00:04:03.583
In this capillary above is the plasma
and below the red blood cells.